2026-05-16T19:18:54.5629428Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T19:18:54.5630301Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T19:18:54.5631052Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T19:18:54.5631829Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T19:18:54.5657629Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T19:18:54.5658571Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T19:18:54.5659471Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-16T19:18:54.5660248Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
